      <title>俄罗斯威胁促使欧盟贷款部门考虑为防御提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/russian-threat-spurs-eu-s-lending-arm-to-look-at-funding-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲投资银行正在考虑如何扩大对国防工业的支持，此举将有助于欧盟加强安全，应对来自俄罗斯日益增长的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/russian-threat-spurs-eu-s-lending-arm-to-look-at-funding-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:51:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>种族主义争议激怒保守党，苏纳克拒绝退还捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sunak-refuses-to-return-donation-as-racism-row-embroils-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)不顾压力，将一名商人向其保守党退还1000万英镑(1280万美元)的捐款，首相谴责这名商人过去对反对派政客发表“种族主义”言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sunak-refuses-to-return-donation-as-racism-row-embroils-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙最大雇主敦促各党在选举后就改革达成一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/portugal-s-biggest-employer-urges-parties-to-agree-on-reforms-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙最大的私营部门雇主 Sonae SGPS SA 希望该国各政党确保稳定，并在可能产生少数派政府的选举后就关键改革达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/portugal-s-biggest-employer-urges-parties-to-agree-on-reforms-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:45:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前联邦调查局间谍被指控亨特·拜登撒谎诱骗银行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/ex-fbi-spy-charged-with-hunter-biden-lie-ensnared-a-bank-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这名前联邦调查局线人被指控谎称亨特·拜登从一家乌克兰能源公司收受数百万美元的贿赂，他也是美国针对一位著名奥地利人的案件背后的间谍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/ex-fbi-spy-charged-with-hunter-biden-lie-ensnared-a-bank-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>资助民主党的 Loral 首席执行官伯纳德·L·施瓦茨 (Bernard L. Schwartz) 去世，享年 98 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/bernard-l-schwartz-loral-ceo-who-funded-democrats-dies-at-98</link>
      <description><![CDATA[劳拉公司 (Loral Corp.) 的长期负责人伯纳德·L·施瓦茨 (Bernard L. Schwartz) 去世，他在比尔·克林顿 (Bill Clinton) 总统任期内成为美国民主党最大的财政支持者之一。他98岁了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/bernard-l-schwartz-loral-ceo-who-funded-democrats-dies-at-98</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着候选人跟随观众，流媒体电视上的政治广告激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/political-ads-surge-on-streaming-tv-as-candidates-follow-viewers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本月“超级星期二”初选前几天，洛杉矶华特迪士尼公司 Hulu 流媒体服务的观众看到了大量政治广告，内容涵盖从美国参议院候选人到市议会席位之争等各种内容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/political-ads-surge-on-streaming-tv-as-candidates-follow-viewers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
